How Your Automated Tool Should Run These Tests

Workflow:

1. Crawl site and collect endpoints
2. Identify authenticated endpoints
3. Capture session/token
4. Modify IDs and roles
5. Send requests automatically
6. Compare responses
7. Detect unauthorized access
8. Generate vulnerability report
